Gii thiu

JADE GARDEN HILL

Jade Garden Hill l d nt nn Bit th Vn Sinh Thi Bo Lcti 134 Phng Hng, Phng Lc Tin, Thnh Ph Bo Lc. D n Jade Garden Hill c quy m 57 nn bit th, vi din tch t: 10m x22m, 10m x 25m. Php l : S ring tng l, c th chuyn th c 100%. ng ni b rng 6m. Thnh ph Bo Lc ang cho n rt nhiu nh u t ln nh trong thi gian gn y.

L Thnh Ph hin ang c mc gi nh t thp nht so vi cc thnh ph ln cn nh Phan Thit, Bin Ha, Lt, Bnh Dngu t vo BS Bo Lc s cn t vn hn nhiu so vi cc khu vc khc, nn nhng nh u t nh l cng d dng tham gia. Th trng BS Bo Lc hi t cc nhn t gm : Ch u T, Sn Phn Phi, Mi Gii, Khch hng nn trong thi gian ti s rt si ng.

V TR D N JADE GARDEN HILL BO LC
V tr Jade Garden Hill nm ngay ti 134 Phng Hng, Phng Lc Tin, Thnh Ph Bo Lc, Tnh Lm ng. Phng Lc Tin nm k cn phng 2, mt 7 pht di chuyn v trung tm Bo Lc. Khch u t khi v Bo Lc thng s u tin mua t cc Phng hn so vi cc Huyn hay cc X.

Sp ti s m thm tuyn ng kt ni Nguyn An Ninh, Nguyn Tri Phng v Phng Hng, di chuyn t Jade Garden Hill s thun tin hn rt nhiu.

Khi Bo Lc tr thnh th ph ca Lm ng, c quan hnh chnh s tp trung v ng Hunh Thc Khng, cch Jade Garden Hill ch 3,5 km.

Nm trn hng di chuyn t Trung tm Bo Lc n Dambri v ngc li. Trong tng lai hng Ty ca Bo Lc s c s pht trin nhanh hn so vi cc hng khc khi Cao Tc Du Giy Lin Khng c trin khai.

Kt ni giao thng t Jade Garden Hill:
i Thnh ph H Ch Minh: 190 km.
Ti Lt : 110 km.
Ti Phan Thit : 100 km.
Ti sn bay Lin Khng : 70 km.
Xe khch : Thnh Bi, Phng Trang 24/7, 30 pht c 1 chuyn.
Cao tc Du Giy Lin Khng : Trin khai giai on 2021-2025.
Pht trin du lch Thnh Ph Bo Lc:
V a hnh, Bo Lc c nhiu i ni, sng h rt thch hp Pht trin du lch. Lng khch hng di chuyn t cc tnh pha Nam ti Lt rt ng v thng dng chn ti Bo Lc.

Thi gian ti s c nhiu ch u t tham gia pht trin Bt ng Sn du lch ti Bo Lc nh Him Lam, Hng Thnh, Sun Group, Novaland.

Du lch pht trin mnh s thc y kinh t tng trng rt nhanh, bn cnh cng gp phn lm gia tng gi tr Bt ng Sn.

Kinh t pht trin cng thc y s pht trin ca h tng giao thng ti Bo Lc.
